                       <div class="summary">
              
            Flowers make a nice gift to the friend that needs a smile or for that special someone in your life. Roses are even better. But sometimes even roses don't cut it. Sometimes you need something a little more non-clich&eacute;, something...extraordinary... Sometimes, you need BACON.<br />

          
